# Environment Configuration

## Frontend (.env)

If you need to customize the API endpoint, add a `.env` file in the root of the TaskManager-Frontend directory:

```
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
```

## Backend (Ensure it's running)

Make sure the backend is running on `http://localhost:5000` before starting the frontend development server.

The backend should have the following endpoints:
- `POST /api/auth/register` - Register new user
- `POST /api/auth/login` - Login user
- `GET /api/tasks` - Get all tasks
- `POST /api/tasks` - Create new task
- `PUT /api/tasks/{id}` - Update task
- `DELETE /api/tasks/{id}` - Delete task
- `PUT /api/tasks/{id}/toggle` - Toggle task completion status
